---

**직접 검증 방법:**
- HackerOne: `https://hackerone.com/directory/programs` → `Sort: Launched (Newest)` + `Offers Bounties` 필터
- Bugcrowd: `https://www.bugcrowd.com/bug-bounty-list/` → `New` 탭 필터
- GitHub 데이터: `https://github.com/arkadiyt/bounty-targets-data` → `data/bugcrowd_data.json` (커밋 diff로 최근 추가 프로그램 확인)

Sources:
- [Bugcrowd Bug Bounty List](https://www.bugcrowd.com/bug-bounty-list/)
- [HackerOne Bug Bounty Programs](https://www.hackerone.com/bug-bounty-programs)
