- [Neon Bug Bounty Goes Public](https://neon.com/blog/neons-bug-bounty-program-with-hackerone-goes-public)
- [9 top bug bounty programs launched in 2025 - CSO Online](https://www.csoonline.com/article/657751/top-bug-bounty-programs.html)
- [bounty-targets-data (arkadiyt)](https://github.com/arkadiyt/bounty-targets-data)
